creator: E-LASTIC EQUIPAMENTOS E SERVICOS DE MEDICAO LTDA
descriptionHtml:
USERS
You can register your patients and track their evolution individually. In addition to having specific strength assessment protocols, you will also have the option to assemble your protocols for each patient.

INTENSITY CONTROL
Know the proper workout load for each patient or student. In addition, quantify any elastic implements or springs during exercise.

REPORTS
Record and track your treatment with charts. The app allows you to send progress reports with your logo to the patient, doctor or other professional through e-mail.

PORTABILITY
The E-lastic is portable and can be attached to different locations, allowing you to take your kit anywhere, offering the best of your patient care.

NEWS
In the 5.0 version we will present the following new features:
- Simultaneous use of the app by different professionals;
- Asymmetry graphs;
- Insertion of logo in reports;
- 3 languages: Portuguese, English and Spanish;
- Usability improvements in general;
- Option of adding trainings to your favorites;
- TV mode.
descriptionShort: E-lastic is a complete system for assessing muscular strength.

We know that you are a distinguished professional and are always looking for updates. That is why I am introducing version 6.0 of the E-lastic application.

Create protocols, exercises, manage patients and evaluators, organize them with labels, evaluate strength, and share the results directly with them through customized reports with your logo. All this in a few minutes.

title: E-lastic

container.value:
SIG, quadra 1, lotes 985/1055
Centro Empresarial Parque Brasília, sala 142
Zona Industrial, Sudoeste/Octogonal, CEP 70.610-410
Brasília/DF

creator: E-LASTIC EQUIPAMENTOS E SERVICOS DE MEDICAO LTDA
descriptionHtml:
USERS
You can register your patients and track their evolution individually. In addition to having specific strength assessment protocols, you will also have the option to assemble your protocols for each patient.

INTENSITY CONTROL
Know the proper workout load for each patient or student. In addition, quantify any elastic implements or springs during exercise.

REPORTS
Record and track your treatment with charts. The app allows you to send progress reports with your logo to the patient, doctor or other professional through e-mail.

PORTABILITY
The E-lastic is portable and can be attached to different locations, allowing you to take your kit anywhere, offering the best of your patient care.

NEWS
In this version we will present the following new features:
- Simultaneous use of the app by different professionals;
- Asymmetry graphs;
- Insertion of logo in reports;
- 3 languages: Portuguese, English and Spanish;
- Usability improvements in general;
- Option of adding trainings to your favorites;
- TV mode.
descriptionShort: E-lastic is a complete system for assessing muscular strength.

descriptionHtml:
USERS
You can register your patients and track their evolution individually. In addition to having specific strength assessment protocols, you will also have the option to assemble your protocols for each patient.

INTENSITY CONTROL
Know the proper workout load for each patient or student. In addition, quantify any elastic implements or springs during exercise.

REPORTS
Record and track your treatment with charts. The app allows you to send progress reports with your logo to the patient, doctor or other professional through e-mail.

PORTABILITY
The E-lastic is portable and can be attached to different locations, allowing you to take your kit anywhere, offering the best of your patient care.

NEWS
In this version we will present the following new features:
- Simultaneous use of the app by different professionals;
- Asymmetry graphs;
- Insertion of logo in reports;
- 3 languages: Portuguese, English and Spanish;
- Usability improvements in general;
- Option of adding trainings to your favorites;
- TV mode.
descriptionShort: E-lastic is a complete system for assessing muscular strength.
